1
00:00:17,980 --> 00:00:19,180
Korn.

2
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:21,780
Dal by som si zmrzlinu.

3
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,800
Prečo ti chutia také zvláštne veci?

4
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:28,240
Zmrzlina je zvláštna?

5
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:30,240
Však som ti ani nepovedal,
akú chcem príchuť.

6
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:33,460
Tentokrát si dám...

7
00:00:33,460 --> 00:00:35,460
čokoládovú príchuť.

8
00:00:41,580 --> 00:00:43,640
Poďme na výlet.

9
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:46,400
Poďme do Kanchanaburi.

10
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:48,480
Videl som to miesto v seriáli.

11
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:51,120
Hlavný pár tam mal veľa romantických scén.

12
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:54,080
Bolo to roztomilé.

13
00:00:56,260 --> 00:00:57,640
Zase hovoríš samé nezmysli.

14
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,520
Pozeráš až priveľa seriálov.

15
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,640
Ďakujeme.

16
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:21,080
Poďme, Korn.

17
00:01:39,860 --> 00:01:40,780
Dean.

18
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,200
Kam mám ísť?

19
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,000
Patrím iba tebe.

20
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:26,440
Chýbal si mi.

21
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:28,860
Chýbal si mi, Dean.

22
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,240
Aj ty si mi chýbal.

23
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,580
Veľmi si mi chýbal.

24
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:36,600
Prepáč.

25
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,040
Prepáč.

26
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,080
Prepáč, že som ťa nechal čakať.

27
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,780
To nevadí, môj chlapček.

28
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,720
To nevadí.

29
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:48,840
Som tu.

30
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,780
Som tu s tebou.

31
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,580
Mal som sen.

32
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:05,080
Videl som Korn-a a Intouch-a.

33
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:09,920
Už sú šťastní.

34
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,360
Sú veľmi šťastní.

35
00:04:15,820 --> 00:04:17,420
Sú konečne šťastní.

36
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:25,840
Už mi to nikdy neurob.

37
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,420
Poďme.

38
00:04:43,740 --> 00:04:44,680
Dean.

39
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,500
Čo to robíš?

40
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:48,580
Musíme dohnať ten čas,
kedy sme boli od seba.

41
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,020
Pusť ma!

42
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:51,020
Nehýb sa.

43
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:52,660
Ak sa budeš hýbať,
pustím ťa.

44
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:57,420
Dobrý chlapec.

45
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,800
Poďme.

46
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,980
Dean!

47
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,480
Pusť ma.

48
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,460
Dean.

49
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,400
Čo chceš robiť?

50
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:12,300
Musím ťa potrestať.

51
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:13,960
Dean.

52
00:05:16,740 --> 00:05:18,040
Dean.

53
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,560
Dean.

54
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:23,340
Prestaň.

55
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,360
Dean.

56
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:39,140
Prepáč, že som ťa nechal tak dlho čakať.

57
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,600
Už som si istý,

58
00:05:56,020 --> 00:05:57,760
že...

59
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:01,780
je...

60
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:03,720
naša láska...

61
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:07,060
skutočná.

62
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:55,740
Si unavený?

63
00:06:58,180 --> 00:06:59,940
Chýbal si mi.

64
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,760
To ty si si chcel dať pauzu.

65
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,540
Bol som zmätený.

66
00:07:12,700 --> 00:07:14,020
A čo teraz?

67
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,420
Milujem ťa.

68
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:21,800
Naozaj?

69
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,140
Ako veľmi ma miluješ?

70
00:07:23,140 --> 00:07:25,140
Veľmi ťa milujem.

71
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,200
Aj ja ťa milujem.

72
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,520
Posledné tri mesiace...

73
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:41,480
som premýšľal nad viacerými vecami.

74
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,700
Zmenil som si moje priezvisko.

75
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:49,100
Huh?

76
00:07:49,940 --> 00:07:51,500
Zmenil si si priezvisko?

77
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:56,100
Prečo?
Aké je tvoje nové priezvisko?

78
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:07,140
Už nie som Rattanon Wongnate.

79
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,200
Už som...

80
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:13,160
Rattanon Chatphokin.

81
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:22,340
To priezvisko...

82
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:24,340
Je to Intouch-ovo priezvisko.

83
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,020
Áno.

84
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:31,960
Chcem sa tým ospravedlniť jeho otcovi.

85
00:08:34,059 --> 00:08:36,879
A taktiež Intouch-ovi.

86
00:08:43,580 --> 00:08:45,000
Neplač.

87
00:08:54,580 --> 00:08:56,260
Neboj sa.

88
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,760
Ďakujem.

89
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,400
Urob pre mňa niečo.

90
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,760
Podáš mi moju peňaženku?

91
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:27,060
Otvor ju.

92
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:41,280
Vedel si, že som to ja.

93
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,980
Pravdaže.

94
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,800
Vyber tú fotku.

95
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,260
Prsteň?

96
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,080
Intouch-ov prsteň.

97
00:10:18,820 --> 00:10:20,540
Je to rodinný klenot.

98
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:24,060
Predáva sa každému mužskému členovi.

99
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:25,980
A...

100
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,000
Teraz...

101
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:31,000
som aj ja oficiálnym členom.

102
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:51,720
Vyzerá možno ošarpane,

103
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,720
no je to najcennejšia vec,

104
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:57,760
akú ti teraz môžem dať.

105
00:11:35,980 --> 00:11:37,500
Po skončení našej školy...

106
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:39,080
začneme spolu žiť.

107
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:43,580
Dobre.

108
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:47,920
Navždy spolu.

109
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:50,360
Áno.

110
00:11:51,940 --> 00:11:53,760
Už nás nikdy nič nerozdelí.

111
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,000
Nikdy.

112
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:34,000
<i>KONIEC</i>

113
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:40,000
<i>Titulky preložilo Škaredé Káčatko</i>

